---
title: Thyme Chicken Thighs and Blistered Tomato Pan Sauce with Caramelized Onions and Garlic Mashed Potatoes
description: Rich and flavourful thyme chicken is the perfect match for a silky caramelized onion and blistered tomato pan sauce. Creamy, garlicky mashed potatoes spruce up this chicken dinner!
